    "introduction": "Jean-Stéphane Bron is a Swiss documentary filmmaker and screenwriter. His films deal with political issues: the crisis of democracy, the economic crisis, the rise of populism. Cleveland Versus Wall Street (2010) was nominated for a César. With The Paris Opera (2017), he won the Swiss Film Award for Best Documentary for the third time. He is a producer with Bande à part Films, alongside Ursula Meier, Lionel Baier, and Frédéric Mermoud.",
